(text "NOTES:" (at 20.32 421.64 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid fcbd9e23-6e69-42d5-b59e-11bb281fb4d1))
(text "Use MX6C-T3NB Cherry MX ULP tactile switches. The project footprint has unnumbered mechanical solder tabs; only switch pins 1/2 enter the matrix." (at 20.32 429.26 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 022c0e83-fe85-405e-aae4-30dbf14fd108))
(text "D320-D384 are 1N4148W/SOD-323 class signal diodes. Diode pin 2 is anode on KB_ROWn; pin 1 is cathode at the per-key switch node." (at 20.32 436.88 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 68840ece-d2f9-4bb0-9866-e5084733fc6f))
(text "J320 keeps the current 30-pin motherboard connector. KB_ROW5..7 and KB_COL14..15 are unused on this 65-key layout and may become spare EC GPIO." (at 20.32 444.5 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 9dbfdfde-f411-40c8-bb23-2a2da075e160))
(text "MX ULP hotswap is not planned: use stencil + reflow/hot plate for production and validate rework on a small coupon first." (at 20.32 452.12 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 25f02d93-803d-48b2-9248-d1880e283b96))
(text "Use split space in rev A. Treat Backspace, Enter, left Shift, and both Space keys as mechanical stabilizer/keycap-risk items before full board release." (at 20.32 459.74 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid d7749ac8-5ab3-420c-8ff1-075e6c0f2a9e))
(text "Legends/keycaps are mechanical deliverables: prototype blank resin/MJF caps and clip coupons before final legends or stabilizer bars." (at 20.32 467.36 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 4c558c30-955c-4af6-8f3c-75a5f677921d))
